OL,6,FTattoos are not an uncommon sight
OL,7,Fparticularly as the weather gets
OL,8,Fwarmer and more skin is on show.
OL,10,FBut it seems more and more people in
OL,11,FWales have some regrets about getting
OL,12,Fa tattoo or around the design they
OL,13,Finitially selected.
